race.comment: STEIN (14) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in both starts to date and strikes a very winnable contest here. Has been well in the betting in both career outings and where there's smoke there's fire. Looks the one they all have to run down. RIGHTEOUS LEGEND (1) has been consistent without winning hitting the top-five in all eight career efforts. Has placed two from two over this six-furlong journey and should be right there at the business end. LINWAR (4) resumes here but has placed two from three when first-up and can run a race while fresh. ANCIENT SCENT (7) strips fitter third-up from the break and may earn some minor money. ZOU ZOU SHARGUSA (6) is on debut and any market confidence must be noted.
